name: Rude Pickle My Face Hydrogel Cucumber Mask
Description: Hydrogel cucumber mask is composed of natural vegetable polymers which provide excellent skin adhesion. As a response to the body's temperature of 36.5 C, the active moisturizing ingredients work inside out. Mask will deliver excellent skin coverage and the active ingredient is gradually absorbed as the gel becomes thin during application.
